<div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-cell left-hand-side" style="" data-widget-type="cell" data-x="0" data-w="12">

<div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-17 ">
<div class="row-fluid ">
<div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget " style="" data-widget-type="custom_widget" data-x="0" data-w="12">
<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_module_15337290032632404" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module widget-type-blog_content" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module">
    <div class="blog-section">
    <div class="blog-post-wrapper">
       <div class="blog-section">
            <div class="blog-post-wrapper cell-wrapper">
                <div class="section post-header">
                    <h1><span id="hs_cos_wrapper_name" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_meta_field hs_cos_wrapper_type_text" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="meta_field" data-hs-cos-type="text">Cloudera - The Rise of Cognitive Computing: Machine Learning, AI and IoT</span></h1>
                  <h4>Written by <a class="author-link" href="https://www.coriniumintelligence.com/insights/author/corinium">Corinium</a> on Dec 6, 2018 1:34:28 AM</h4>
                    
                     <p id="hubspot-topic_data">
                        
                            <a class="post-item-topic-link topic-seq-1" href="https://www.coriniumintelligence.com/insights/topic/cdao"><i class="fa fa-tag" aria-hidden="true"></i> CDAO</a>
                        
                            <a class="post-item-topic-link topic-seq-2" href="https://www.coriniumintelligence.com/insights/topic/cdo"><i class="fa fa-tag" aria-hidden="true"></i> CDO</a>
                        
                            <a class="post-item-topic-link topic-seq-3" href="https://www.coriniumintelligence.com/insights/topic/data-analytics"><i class="fa fa-tag" aria-hidden="true"></i> Data Analytics</a>
                        
                            <a class="post-item-topic-link topic-seq-4" href="https://www.coriniumintelligence.com/insights/topic/cloudera"><i class="fa fa-tag" aria-hidden="true"></i> Cloudera</a>
                        
                            <a class="post-item-topic-link topic-seq-5" href="https://www.coriniumintelligence.com/insights/topic/machine-learning"><i class="fa fa-tag" aria-hidden="true"></i> Machine Learning</a>
                        
                            <a class="post-item-topic-link topic-seq-6" href="https://www.coriniumintelligence.com/insights/topic/trending-cdo"><i class="fa fa-tag" aria-hidden="true"></i> Trending CDO</a>
                        
                            <a class="post-item-topic-link topic-seq-7" href="https://www.coriniumintelligence.com/insights/topic/analytics"><i class="fa fa-tag" aria-hidden="true"></i> Analytics</a>
                        
                            <a class="post-item-topic-link topic-seq-8" href="https://www.coriniumintelligence.com/insights/topic/artificial-intelligence"><i class="fa fa-tag" aria-hidden="true"></i> Artificial Intelligence</a>
                        
                            <a class="post-item-topic-link topic-seq-9" href="https://www.coriniumintelligence.com/insights/topic/cao"><i class="fa fa-tag" aria-hidden="true"></i> CAO</a>
                        
                            <a class="post-item-topic-link topic-seq-10" href="https://www.coriniumintelligence.com/insights/topic/trending-cao"><i class="fa fa-tag" aria-hidden="true"></i> Trending CAO</a>
                        
                            <a class="post-item-topic-link topic-seq-11" href="https://www.coriniumintelligence.com/insights/topic/data"><i class="fa fa-tag" aria-hidden="true"></i> data</a>
                        
                            <a class="post-item-topic-link topic-seq-12" href="https://www.coriniumintelligence.com/insights/topic/artificial-intelligence-machine-learning"><i class="fa fa-tag" aria-hidden="true"></i> Artificial Intelligence &amp; Machine Learning</a>
                        
                            <a class="post-item-topic-link topic-seq-13" href="https://www.coriniumintelligence.com/insights/topic/information-security-iot"><i class="fa fa-tag" aria-hidden="true"></i> Information Security &amp; IoT</a>
                        
                     </p>
                
                 </div>
                
                <div class="section post-body">
                    <span id="hs_cos_wrapper_post_body" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_meta_field hs_cos_wrapper_type_rich_text" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="meta_field" data-hs-cos-type="rich_text"><h2 class="header">Download the Report</h2>
<div class="contact-form row-fluid" data-animation-type="fadeInUp">
<p>Machine learning and artificial intelligence are changing the very meaning of data analytics. Some say the rise of AI and machine learning heralds a new industrial revolution.</p>
<p>With widespread adoption of machine learning, most organisations are still in the early stages with the technology.</p>
<p>The Internet of Things keeps rapidly expending as well. Recent estimates from Juniper Research put IoT growth at 140% within the next 4 years, growing from 21 billion connected devices to 50 billion during that time.</p>
<p>One thing is certain: IoT is generating enormous quantities of data.</p>
<p>Download the report to explore these two technologies as they converge and the impact on organisations.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
</div>
<!--more-->
